Inbox ~/.mail/martin/inbox

Channel work-inbox
Far :work-remote:
Near :work-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel work-sent
Far :work-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :work-local:sent

Channel work-trash
Far :work-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Near :work-local:trash

Group work
